title: HOUR 1 - Mayfield, Cowboys, Wilson, Patriots

description:
Baker Mayfield isn't the problem in Cleveland

The Cowboys are better when they don't rely on Dak Prescott as much

You can't compare Zach Wilson with Josh Allen

Patriots can't seem to take advantage of the cultural change in the NFL
